sf_uiModel.markdownText:
This dashboard provide information per project/tenant. Users can always filter the details by selecting the project/tenant name at global filter.
1. Available cores and used cores
2. Available memory and used memory
3. Available instances and used instances

#####_Note: The below metrics for Neutron component are shown for all projects and are same across all the projects_

1. Number of networks, routers and subnets created
2. Available Floating IPs and used Floating IPs 
3. Available Security groups and used security groups
